            <scopecontent id="aspace_7488f4d788d32a90531002ac831673f0">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series comprises biographical and genealogical materials on the Allen family. The majority of the series was created by Walter Hinds Allen, with exception of a compilation of obituaries about and tributes to his father, Walter Allen. Biographical materials include Allen's school notes, journal entries and the obituaries. Genealogical materials consist of several genealogical charts of different branches of the family and research notes.</p>
            </scopecontent>
